    "<p>Author and curator of Greek art, Metropolitan Museum, 1929-1952.": [],
    "Richter was the daughter of the eminent art historian <a href=\"/richterj\">Jean Paul Richter</a> and <a href=\"/richterl\">Louise Marie Schwaab Richter</a>, also an art historian.": [],
