    "Her 1942 book <em>Kouroi: Archaic Greek Youths</em> and <em>Korai: Archaic Greek Maidens</em>, 1968, remain her most consulted work.": [],
    "Her sister, <a href=\"/richteri\">Irma A. Richter</a>, an artist and art historian collaborated with her on several books.": [],
    "G. M. A. Richter also published on vase painting, jewelry and furniture.": [],
    "While subsequent scholarship has altered her dating somewhat, her chronology of work has not been seriously challenged.": [],
    "In 1946 she hired the young <a href=\"/bothmerd\">Dietrich von Bothmer</a>.": [
